purpose.p:
     The Interface module satisfies the requirement to manage interfaces between products (see Figure 1).  An interface is the interaction between co-functioning
products, or a product and its environment, and, in order to ensure repeatability, is the subject of an .  The specification defines the
product attributes that are necessary to exist at a common boundary.

       Some product attributes:



		fuel flow rate;



		required speed;



		operating temperature;



		physical shape;



		dimensional tolerance.



     In some industry sectors, an  is referred to as an
     Interface Control Document or Drawing.

The interaction of two interfaced products is represented by an . Many types of interaction are possible.
Some interactions:
physical interaction, such as two mechanical gears meshing;
optical interaction, such as an infrared connection between a remote control and a television;
electrical interaction, such as the current at 240 volts, 50 hertz from a domestic supply as required by a refrigerator.

example.screen:
#2000= PRODUCT('Panel power supply',' ','Interface identity for record purposes only',(#2020));
#2010= PRODUCT_RELATED_PRODUCT_CATEGORY('interface',$,(#2000));
#2020= PRODUCT_CONTEXT('marine',#2030,'interface management');
#2030= APPLICATION_CONTEXT('Product life-cycle support');
#2040= PRODUCT_RELATED_PRODUCT_CATEGORY('IFS','Category',(#2000));
#2050= PRODUCT_RELATED_PRODUCT_CATEGORY('POWER','Type',(#2000));

#2070= PRODUCT('420V 50Hz','power supply connector',$,(#2020));
#2080= PRODUCT('Panel RG 431','alarm panel connector',$,(#2020));
#2090= PRODUCT_RELATED_PRODUCT_CATEGORY('interface connector',$,(#2070,#2080));

#2110= INTERFACE_CONNECTOR_AS_REALIZED('420V 50Hz - A',$,#2070);
#2120= INTERFACE_CONNECTOR_AS_REALIZED('Panel RG 431 - A',$,#2080);
#2130= INTERFACE_CONNECTOR_DESIGN_TO_REALIZED('Panel RG 431 - A design',' ',$,#2100,#2120);

#2140= PRODUCT_DEFINITION('420V 50Hz - A',$,#2110,#2220);
#2150= PRODUCT_DEFINITION('Panel RG 431 - A',$,#2120,#2220);
#2160= PRODUCT('Panel RG 431','alarm panel',$,(#2020));
#2170= PRODUCT('420V 50Hz','power supply',$,(#2020));
#2180= PRODUCT_AS_REALIZED('Panel RG 431 - A',$,#2160);
#2190= PRODUCT_AS_REALIZED('420V 50Hz - A',$,#2170);
#2200= PRODUCT_DEFINITION('Panel RG 431 - A',$,#2180,#2220);
#2210= PRODUCT_DEFINITION('420V 50Hz - A',$,#2190,#2220);
#2220= PRODUCT_DEFINITION_CONTEXT('operational configuration',#2030,'in-service');
#2230= PRODUCT_RELATED_PRODUCT_CATEGORY('part',$,(#2160,#2170));
#2240= CONNECTOR_ON('420V 50Hz - A',' ',$,#2140,#2210);
#2250= CONNECTOR_ON('Panel RG 431 - A',' ',$,#2150,#2200);
